ian" lang="hu" hreflang="hu" data-title="Bordeaux-i borvidék" data-language-autonym="Magyar" data-language-local-name="Hungarian" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Magyar</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ml mw-list-item"><a href="https://ml.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E0%B4%AC%E0%B5%8B%E0%B5%BC%E0%B4%A1%E0%B5%8B_%E0%B4%B5%E0%B5%80%E0%B4%9E%E0%B5%8D%E0%B4%9E%E0%B5%8D" title="ബോർഡോ വീഞ്ഞ് – Malayalam" lang="ml" hreflang="ml" data-title="ബോർഡോ വീഞ്ഞ്" data-language-autonym="മലയാളം" data-language-local-name="Malayalam" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>മലയാളം</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-nl mw-list-item"><a href="https://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bordeaux_(wijnstreek)" title="Bordeaux (wijnstreek) – Dutch" lang="nl" hreflang="nl" data-title="Bordeaux (wijnstreek)" data-language-autonym="Nederlands" data-language-local-name="Dutch" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Nederlands</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ja badge-Q17437798 badge-goodarticle mw-list-item" title="good article"><a href="https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%83%9C%E3%83%AB%E3%83%89%E3%83%BC%E3%83%AF%E3%82%A4%E3%83%B3" title="ボルドーワイン – Japanese" lang="ja" hreflang="ja" data-title="ボルドーワイン" data-language-autonym="日本語" data-language-local-name="Japanese" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>日本語</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-no mw-list-item"><a href="https://no.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bordeaux_(vin)" title="Bordeaux (vin) – Norwegian Bokmål" lang="nb" hreflang="nb" data-title="Bordeaux (vin)" data-language-autonym="Norsk bokmål" data-language-local-name="Norwegian Bokmål" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Norsk bokmål</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-nrm mw-list-item"><a href="https://nrm.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vins_de_Bordiaux" title="Vins de Bordiaux – Norman" lang="nrf" hreflang="nrf" data-title="Vins de Bordiaux" data-language-autonym="Nouormand" data-language-local-name="Norman" class="